{
  "title": "Raw Peruvian Garlic Nigiri",
  "description": "A sick-day inspired Peruvian dish made with raw garlic and shaped like nigiri. This dish is ayurvedic-tamasic friendly and has a briny, glassy-jelly texture.",
  "cuisine": "Peruvian",
